Slash(4*(n-1))就會出;<br />\n<br />\nfunction void printSlash(int qty)<br />\n{<br />\n<br />\nfor(int i=0;i&lt;qty;i++)<br />\n{<br />\nSystem.out.print(&quot;/&quot;); <br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n}"},{"pid":"e24f5001d498ce4f4d09eff4c4659ebc1b3bda16","tid":447473,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>while(n&gt;1) { System.out.print(&quot;\\/\\/\\/\\/&quot;); n--; }</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該call printSlash(4*(n-1))就會出;<br />\n<br />\nfunction void printSlash(int qty)<br />\n{<br />\n<br />\nfor(int i=0;i&lt;qty;i++)<br />\n{<br />\nSystem.out.print(&quot;/&quot;); <br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n}</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知syntax啱唔啱<br />\n我寫C#比較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e790cedc1c7926e82402a43144b88b6c8c1b7f","tid":447473,"uid":48491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"System.out.println((new String(new char[4 * (n - 1)])).replace('\\0', '/'));"},{"pid":"7f1771e465ee99a0ca6ebf1144a7f777f8e6ba4b","tid":447473,"uid":48491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>System.out.println((new String(new char[4 * (n - 1)])).replace('\\0', '/'));</blockquote><br />\nnew char[4 * (n - 1)]：整個長度係4 * (n - 1)嘅新字元陣列&mdash;&mdash;元素預設值為空值<br />\nnew String(char[])：用該字元陣列組成一個新字串<br />\nString.replace('\\0', '/')：將該字串的所有空值替換成'/'<br />\nSystem.out.println(String)：列印字串"}]}